data.description: Welcome home to 12215 Spanish Blvd! This multi-level 3 bed, 2 bath home is surrounded by a park-like setting and backs to property owned by St. Louis County! Home has been updated by current owners and taken care of with lots of TLC. Some of the updates include an added 2nd bath on main level, main level laundry, fresh paint, tile flooring, updated kitchen with separate dining area, whirlpool tub and shower and much much more! This rare gem is truly a must-see! Seller is offering a 1 year HSA Home Warranty! Schedule your showing today! Seller is selling the home as-is and will do no repairs or inspections.
